Please be advised that Change Healthcare has become aware of suspicious activities whereby unknown, non-Change Healthcare-affiliated groups are using the Change Healthcare name and logos in employment scams. Click here to find out more.
Meet Change Healthcare.

We’re a dynamic organization that helps healthcare entities connect, transact and communicate. Our Intelligent Healthcare NetworkTM connects payers, providers, pharmacies and patients so they can more effectively and efficiently interact with each other. A lot of this is centered on helping providers and pharmacies get paid by payers and patients quickly and completely. On the flip side, for payers and patients, we help deliver their payments while helping them reduce their risk of overpaying.

In addition to helping all of the stakeholders in the care continuum move data from point A to point B, we also translate, edit and analyze that data when needed, and then help mine that wealth of information to improve healthcare through insights. We do all of this using a combination of technology and services.

If that sounds impressive, it should. If you are searching for a career where you can make a lasting impact on the lives, well-being and health of all Americans, Change Healthcare is the place for you. We invite you to take a look at all of our open positions to learn more about the skills we need.


In addition to what we do, it’s also important to talk about how we choose to do all of that. Cultivating a culture that is guided by our core values is also a top priority and these values are woven into the fabric of every aspect of our company.

To that end, we recruit team members who can model our core values, which include: Customer Centric; Top 10%; Hire and Develop the Best; Think Big, Start Small, Move Fast and Empowerment with Accountability.


Let’s take a closer look at who Change Healthcare is. If you’d like to learn more about:


