ProvidersServing 5,500 hospitals and over 800,000 physicians, our solutions help providers and health system leaders achieve your strategic objectives. We help to enhance patient engagement and access, improve quality outcomes, drive revenue performance, and improve operational efficiencies.We give hospitals and doctors the tools they need to verify patient eligibility in real-time, submit claims electronically, and automate billing systems. End-to-end revenue cycle management workflow and analytics help maximize reimbursement and simplify patient collections. Through our revenue cycle and value-based care services, we help providers scale capabilities and improve margin performance.The industry-leading criteria, InterQual®, is used by the Centers for Medicare & Medicaid Services and over 4,600 hospitals and facilities, covering over 100 million lives to help ensure clinically appropriate care.  Leading radiology and cardiology imaging solutions are used in over 3,300 facilities across the United States and internationally. Delivering Proven PerformanceSt. Luke's Health System increased POS collections 26%, post service collections 6%, and total payment collections by 9.4% using our Network and Payment Solutions. With our Revenue Performance  Solutions, Trinity Health decreased Blue Cross A/R down more than 50%.
UniNet Health Network gained $5 million cost savings in value-based care population and improved patients’ risk scores. 
