Health Care Technology

Company Overview of Change Healthcare Holdings, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Change Healthcare Holdings, Inc., through its subsidiaries, provides software and analytics, network solutions, and technology-enabled services for healthcare market. The company operates in three segments: Software and Analytics, Network Solutions, and Technology-Enabled Services. The Software and Analytics segment offers payment and reimbursement optimization and decision support solutions that include revenue cycle technology, revenue optimization, payment integrity, electronic payment, risk adjustment, quality reporting, data and analytics, and engagement solutions. The Network Solutions segment provides network solutions offerings comprising financial and administrative information exch...
Change Healthcare Holdings, Inc., through its subsidiaries, provides software and analytics, network solutions, and technology-enabled services for healthcare market. The company operates in three segments: Software and Analytics, Network Solutions, and Technology-Enabled Services. The Software and Analytics segment offers payment and reimbursement optimization and decision support solutions that include revenue cycle technology, revenue optimization, payment integrity, electronic payment, risk adjustment, quality reporting, data and analytics, and engagement solutions. The Network Solutions segment provides network solutions offerings comprising financial and administrative information exchange solutions for medical, and pharmacy and dental claims management; and for other standardized healthcare transactions, including clinical information exchange capabilities. The Technology-Enabled Services segment offers payment and communication, workflow, advisory, and other administrative solutions to optimize payment and reimbursement processes. Its technology-enabled services offerings include payment and communication, eligibility and enrollment, healthcare consulting, payment automation, and pharmacy benefits administration solutions. The company was formerly known as Emdeon Inc. and changed its name to Change Healthcare Holdings, Inc. in November 2015. The company was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Nashville, Tennessee. Change Healthcare Holdings, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Change Healthcare Intermediate Holdings, Inc.
